Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:03.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}谛听！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:05.42,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}谛听！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:07.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}谛听！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:09.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}玄离？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:14.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}要等他们散场么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:15.46,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:17.46,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}还是要尽快解决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:18.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}破老
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:20.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}还是麻烦你走一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:24.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}去是没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:26.96,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不过我没法感应天明珠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:29.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}他们已经很久没动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:31.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}在场馆最东南角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:32.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}一只黑猫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:34.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}应该不难找
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:36.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}东南角.....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:39.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那里的确有妖精的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:41.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:43.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我就见机行事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:45.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.91,0:00:47.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}那就靠你了老蛤蟆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:50.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}老蛤蟆？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}他已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:00:58.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}应该就是那只了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:01.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}咦？ 谛听！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:07.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}他应该听到了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:09.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}怎么没反应呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:11.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}你在这干嘛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:13.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}你有见到小白么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:14.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我们在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:16.99,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}是么！太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:19.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}等下可能会有妖精找他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:20.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}已经来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:21.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:32.53,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}阿根小友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:35.32,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}你这样不辞而别
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:38.24,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}是不想遵守你的承诺么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:40.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}我是说过会让他交出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:41.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}小黑，给他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:42.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}哼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:43.32,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:44.24,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}哼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:46.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}你只是不爽我能从你那离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:49.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}你不觉得太无礼了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.61,0:01:51.78,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}难道你那样困住我就很有礼貌？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:56.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}誓言录奖品的抢夺是持有者必须面对的风险
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:58.90,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}这是誓言录的默许规则
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:00.40,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}什么是默许规则？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:02.40,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}只是老君不插手而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:05.03,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}谁都知道老君不会插手世间的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:09.15,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}当有几个人这么说的时候其他人就默认这个是规则了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:13.82,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}说到底也就是给自己创造一个名正言顺的抢劫理由而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:16.99,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}还是说你真的觉得这是合理的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.99,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你昨个不这么说呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:20.74,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}说了被打怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:22.86,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}现在就不怕挨削啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.32,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}现在我有谛听
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:27.74,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}谛听大人不能介入天明珠之事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:28.69,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:29.44,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:32.03,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}难道介入了我还怕你咋的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:33.23,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}老府！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:34.28,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不得无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:38.23,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}哎呀老蛤蟆！你还真当自个是老大呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:40.44,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我瞅这谛听说不定都是假的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:40.98,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}老府！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:43.48,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}啊啊啊啊！烫死啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:45.65,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}谛听大人莫怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:55.57,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}天明珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.40,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你们为什么需要天明珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:58.90,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你不需要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:00.23,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}如果我不交出来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:01.90,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我们只好动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:03.02,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}如果你们动手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:04.40,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我就把它交给谛听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:05.90,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:07.98,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}这样对你有什么好处？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:08.77,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}反正我也保不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:09.73,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}让你们不爽我就爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:15.44,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你们是想试试我能否交到谛听手上么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:17.15,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你们这是串通好的吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:20.31,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我完全不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:23.11,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不过如果能这样收回天明珠倒也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:24.77,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我向你们保证
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:28.23,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}收到天明珠之后我不会还给他的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:35.48,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}青丘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:37.98,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}还是好好的说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:45.19,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.73,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我们并不认同抢夺奖品的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:50.48,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我们的确……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:53.06,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}做了一件违心之事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.14,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}但我们需要天明珠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.77,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}愿意用一切交换
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:02.68,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不知小兄弟可否割爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:03.85,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}原因是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.68,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}救一个朋友的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:09.48,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.89,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}怎么着！小子！我还能骗你咋的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.02,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.43,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}哎呀小兔崽子你是不是不想活啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:20.56,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}他没有说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:21.64,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}你知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:23.27,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}老君怕我被骗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:24.81,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}给了我定心镜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.68,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}哇真方便...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.14,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}那就给他们呗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:31.10,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}如果有这么简单我们就不用这样了小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.39,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你知道天明珠是干啥的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:34.76,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}说给就给？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:36.06,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:40.43,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你愿意把它给我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:41.60,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你们一开始说明不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:43.85,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我们……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:47.18,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}这可是天明珠啊谁能想到你居然会给我们呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.72,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}你难道不知道它是干啥用的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:49.47,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}不要就还我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:52.43,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}惭愧..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.64,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我们就厚颜的收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:56.93,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}如果以后小兄弟你需要我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.80,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}请到会馆告知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:01.14,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我们定当尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.22,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}哈哈哈我们以后就是哥们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:04.97,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.30,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我又开始讨厌你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.51,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我们想尽快带回这个消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.47,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:11.47,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:15.09,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}后会有期啦 小妖精们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:17.68,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:19.51,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}他们不是会馆的人么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.26,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}老君不会帮他们么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:22.88,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}如果那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:26.26,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}天明珠也不会几百年来都没人拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.30,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}那小黑怎么拿到的呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:30.84,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}他的能力合适
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.93,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}而且他挺强的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:35.18,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}难道比哥哥还厉害？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:37.13,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}被我打伤之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.18,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}的确是比现在的玄离强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:40.22,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}哇!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:41.51,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}并没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:41.97,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}唔？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:42.97,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}现在的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.01,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}看来我多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.01,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我先回老君那去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:50.17,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:53.26,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这样随便就给出了天明珠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.42,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}希望你不要后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:01.88,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我是不是说错话了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.01,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}是生小黑的气啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:08.09,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}因为天明珠对他和老君来说是有特殊意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:11.51,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}话说小黑你还真是舍得啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:12.46,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}他们不是比我更需要么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.05,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}天明珠是治病用的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:17.05,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}天明珠只能治一种病
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.92,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}这并不是它吸引人的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:20.42,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}那是什么原因？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:21.84,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}它之所以珍贵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:24.09,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}是因为普通的妖精如果拥有它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.13,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}便可以进化为“仙”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.38,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}诶？
